column1: Cafe Ba-Ba-Reeba!////The only thing that stood out was the dates wrapped in bacon - but let's be honest
column2: everything wrapped in bacon is amazing. The sangria - I had about 4-5 glasses and didn't even have a buzz. Did they forget to put the alcohol in? It was my birthday
column3: I wanted a buzz. Kind of disappointing. I've had way better Sangria.
